<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-latestquestions" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">
  <metal:form use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">

    <metal:extra_info fill-slot="extra_info">
      <div>
      <tal:similar-faqs condition="view/similar_faqs">
        <p i18n:translate="">These FAQs seems similar to your question. Take
          a look at them, you may find your answer in one these.
        </p>
      
        <ul id="similar-faqs" class="faq">
          <li tal:repeat="faq view/similar_faqs"
              tal:attributes="title faq/content/fmt:shorten/320"
              ><a href="#"
                  tal:attributes="here faq/fmt:url"
                  tal:content="faq/title">FAQ Title</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </tal:similar-faqs>
      <tal:similar-questions condition="view/similar_questions">
        <p i18n:translate="">These other questions seem similar to yours. You may want to take a look at them.</p>

        <table id="similar-questions">
          <tbody>
            <tr tal:repeat="question view/similar_questions"
                tal:replace="structure question/@@+listing-detailed" />
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </tal:similar-questions>

      <tal:similar-items condition="view/has_similar_items">
        <p i18n:translate="">If you did not find your problem in these
          existing FAQs or questions, enter the details of your problem
          to alert the
          <tal:displayName content="context/displayname"
                            i18n:name="displayname">Project</tal:displayName>
          support community, so they can help you resolve the issue.
        </p>
      </tal:similar-items>

      <tal:no-similar-items condition="not: view/has_similar_items">
        <p i18n:translate="">There are no existing FAQs or questions similar to
          the summary you entered.
        </p>
        <p i18n:translate="">Enter the details of your problem to alert the
          <tal:displayName content="context/displayname"
                            i18n:name="displayname">Project</tal:displayName>
          support community, so they can help you resolve the issue.
        </p>
      </tal:no-similar-items>

      <tal:comment replace="nothing">
        This link should appear in the appropriate widget description,
        but cannot because of bug #72730.
      </tal:comment>
      <p><a href="/+editmylanguages">Change your
        preferred languages</a> to modify the list of languages available
        for writing the question.
      </p>

      <metal:unsupported_languages_warning
         use-macro="view/unsupported_languages_warning" />
      </div>
    </metal:extra_info>

    <div class="actions" metal:fill-slot="buttons">
      <input tal:replace="structure view/add_action/render" />
    </div>

  </metal:form>
</div>

<metal:help fill-slot="help">
  <ol>
    <li>If any similar FAQs or questions are found, take the time to look
        to see if there is one that is the same as yours.<br />
        <strong>Tip:</strong> Leaving your mouse over the FAQ or question
        title will pop out the beginning of the content.
    </li>
    <li>If there is no similar items or none of them apply to your problem,
      then enter the complete details of your question in the
      <strong>Description</strong> field. Give as much
      context information as possible: steps you have taken to resolve the
      problem, version of the programs you were using, etc. Click the
      <strong>Add</strong> button once you're satisfied with your description.
    </li>
  </ol>
  <p>You can consult the
    <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/GettingSupportInLaunchpad">Getting
      Support in Launchpad</a> document for more information.</p>
  </metal:help>

</body>
</html>

